We will start every meetup with some socializing followed by a quick beginner level topic so we can help each other get started and build our skills. Following that, we will have a break and then a speaker from the community will have an advanced Android talk to so we can take our skills to the next level! Join us as we show Omaha how incredible and supportive the Android community is. See you there!

Please contact the GDG organizers if you would like to start meeting on other Google topics.

We also have a slack!
